Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened? Where am I?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remember we were fighting.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean I died?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is any of this even real?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have I gone to hell?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 12\NLIGHT IN THE DARKNESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture it in your mind clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll leave your body,\Nescaping as a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you've entered\Ninto that dream-state,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.78,0:00:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you will then enter Mr. Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Once there,\Nyour focus will be finding his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:01:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo, be as safe as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! You are absolutely capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here believes in you.\NWe'll be by your side every step.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever I come across there,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come back with Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Saimori house...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For every Grotesquerie\NI cut down, another one emerges.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no sign of Godo\Nor the rest of the team.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't my world at all, is it?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... regardless of where I am,\NI refuse to die here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Lord Kudo...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me? Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean Lord Kudo's in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over here...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This way...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to catch me if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm over here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to hurry and find Lord Kudo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is that here?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... know that door...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The clothes they're wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miyo...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I heard her, so she must be nearby!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was supposed to go back for her...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but she came for me?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I have to see her again to apologize.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will I make it?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I must.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I refuse to die before seeing her again.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will get out of this place!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like me, but who...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're not going\Nto be able to see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not worthy of him,\Nbeing near his light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you'll be alone again forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you... think it's easier that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you've always lived, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You already know.\NThat's the truth, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You disregard his kindness at every turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The only thing you're good at\Nis hurting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Because you're so careless,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}he's wandering in the dark,\Nslipping closer into his grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:07:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Anyone who associates with you\Nis doomed to be unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You know I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's why you have to stay away\Nfrom Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe what you say is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to change myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw everything I did as a failure,\Nso of course I'd agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exactly like you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm so awful,\Nthen I shouldn't be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, that's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that's not what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you have a gift,\Nyou mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I discovered my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because of the people in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,People who care deeply about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of their belief in me\Nthat I think it's all right that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm allowed to stay with Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Lying to yourself again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know how much easier\Nyou think your life would be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,if you were alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're wrong. That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,After Mother died, life was a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had to struggle to survive\Never since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There was never a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The only option was to dull my heart\Nso it wouldn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the only way\NI could handle being alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the only option back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that that was\Nhow I was supposed to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But now... I know\Nmy life won't have to be that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's far too late for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always given up\Nand that's all you'll ever do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not... I decided\Nthat I'm done giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to give up because it's easier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How many more scars do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of person you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't want to hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lord Kudo suffered because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what I did. That's why\NI have to make sure I can apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He's there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Every chance he's had,\Nhe's been on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He never faltered.\NHe's always believed in me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I couldn't see it.\NI didn't believe in myself.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was too afraid that I'd get hurt.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting hurt might seem scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but I won't run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I choose to believe what Lord Kudo says!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That means... I'm going\Nto have to believe in myself
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the way he believes in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to stay with Lord Kudo\Nfor the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.\NI'm going to find Lord Kudo now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That way, you and I\Ncan finally know happiness together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I hope we can. Sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Lord Kudo's hair tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Lord Kudo!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That... Is that your gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to bring you back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. This isn't the end of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mm.\N- However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Faithful servants...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your... Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his state? Is he dead yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, a woman\Nfrom the Usuba family is interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That Usuba brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty,\Nplease don't overexert yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kudos are now\Nan unprecedented threat to us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, it is crucial that we eliminate\Nthe power of Dream-Sight immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, will you please hold my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What I mean is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you believe in me right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home... together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Be gone now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Upon my rule, you both must die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You heard me go on and on\Nabout protecting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but you ended up protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is yours. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find you at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and things were scary,\Nbut this hair tie guided me to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So, is that where it went?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd lost it\Nwhen it fell off in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can put it back on for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,if you wouldn't mind my doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Lord Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}At the Usuba house, do you remember\Nwhen I was asked what I wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I hesitated, but eventually told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}that I did not care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You should know... that was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:16:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... I'm the one\Nwho should be apologizing to you, Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought\NI would do something that would hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I lost my temper\Nand I spoke out of a place of anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I am truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want... is to always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please let me know\NI can be with you forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It was always my intention to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I want to remain close to you\Nif you'd allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes. Of course you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had told me "no",\NI can't imagine what state I'd be in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!\NI'd never say such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Commander!\N- Mr. Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Commander!{\i}\N-{\i1}Young Master, please!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Commander, can you hear me?{\i}\N-{\i1}Please, Kiyoka!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Miyo!{\i}\N-{\i1}Miss Miyo!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Our friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo,\Neveryone's waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}- Commander! I'm begging ya!\N- Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}- Miyo!\N- Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that means... I'm back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're awake! I'm so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to worry you. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I am now, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was so worried about you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Godo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off me, I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Arata, wait!\N- Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... Are you heading back home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It looks like...\Nyou no longer need my protection,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}so there's no reason for me to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You've really... so thank you,\Nbut I feel like there's more to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I only... did\Nwhat any proper person would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can't go back with you.\NThat place isn't my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's really no need for you\Nto apologize for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miyo, you're still... a part of our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So it's you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you know we'll be having a rematch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. You know\Nwhere to find me when you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He what? It was His Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Emperor had lost\Nhis divine revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear of not knowing the future\Nconsumed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He sought to expose the Grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lives were put at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}His acts were\Nboth selfish and unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It is my vow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that every debt will be repaid.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like forever since I last stood\Nin front of this threshold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to see you at the door.\NWelcome, Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm home, Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finally, our daily lives\Nregained a sense of peace.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My nightmares were over.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I no longer suffered\Nfrom sleepless nights.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lord Kudo and I\Ngot to share our meals together,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and enjoy conversing with one another.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm starting to notice...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I no longer dread\Ngoing to sleep or waking up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It feels like I know\Nthe true meaning of happiness now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Getting to cherish little moments\Nwith someone dear to me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SEVERAL DAYS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our blissful days of peace\Npassed by in the blink of an eye.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And before I knew it,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it was time to test\Nall of my training with Miss Hazuki.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope I make her proud.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,PARTY DAY!\NBREAK A LEG, MIYO!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo, I...\NI'm sorry if I kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.28,0:22:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say... you're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to hear you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You... look good.\NYou're very handsome tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so I'm sure it wasn't a dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,can you confirm it for me one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Troublesome kind of fellow\Nas you know I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}did you really say you'll be my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Troublesome? How could you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}when I was always\Nthe one who started trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And you still won't regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Marrying someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I could never regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}After all, we chose each other, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's still a lot I need to learn,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so please be patient with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And you, with me.
